00:02:09.389 --> 00:02:14.060
It's sort of part of her sunny,
absent minded disposition.

00:02:14.060 --> 00:02:15.600
It's kind of cute.

00:02:15.600 --> 00:02:16.860
But not recently.

00:02:16.860 --> 00:02:21.120
Recently, there have been some
