00:02:21.120 --> 00:02:22.860
and some serious scares.

00:02:22.860 --> 00:02:26.294
Tragedy was narrowly
avoided a couple times.

00:02:26.294 --> 00:02:27.960
It seems the problem
has something to do

00:02:27.960 --> 00:02:30.720
with your sibling's eyesight.

00:02:30.720 --> 00:02:33.420
Your mom takes you all to the
