00:29:41.410 --> 00:29:45.080
It's very inspiring.

00:29:45.080 --> 00:29:48.440
It's an autobiography,
yet it's very inspiring.

00:29:48.440 --> 00:29:51.030
I think I found it very useful
and amazing to read through it.

